## Limitations
The analysis is based on available online resources and may not capture all perspectives on job-hopping. The findings are influenced by the publication dates and the specific contexts of the articles reviewed. Additionally, the perception of job-hopping can vary significantly across industries and geographic regions, which may not be fully represented in this report.